&lt;h3 id=&#34;场景2&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#场景2&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 场景 2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reservations and ticket information. May I help you?&lt;br&gt;
 订票服务部，您需要什么服务？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yes. I’d like to confirm my reservation.&lt;br&gt;
 我想确认我订的飞机票。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your date of departure and your flight number, please.&lt;br&gt;
